441
00:23:26,018 --> 00:23:29,820
identifying productive workers
and problem cases.

442
00:23:29,822 --> 00:23:33,590
Pentland: Individuals want to come across
in a way that's effective.

443
00:23:33,592 --> 00:23:36,059
You want to
have people trust you.

444
00:23:36,061 --> 00:23:38,562
You want to
have your ideas heard.

445
00:23:38,564 --> 00:23:41,331
You don't want to be doing
