462
00:24:44,166 --> 00:24:48,301
What if our minds could heal us?

463
00:24:50,738 --> 00:24:52,138
Dr. Herbert Benson,

464
00:24:52,140 --> 00:24:55,842
of the Benson-Henry Institute
