488
00:26:18,693 --> 00:26:20,760
Freeman: It's still unknown

489
00:26:20,762 --> 00:26:24,331
exactly how the monks achieve
this inner fire.

490
00:26:24,333 --> 00:26:26,132
But scientists suspect

491
00:26:26,134 --> 00:26:28,501
the meditation
directly taps into

492
00:26:28,503 --> 00:26:33,506
the part of the nervous system
